main event: An unidentified object was observed by a witness in Hartford, Wisconsin, in June 1966.
interesting points: The object flashed on and off every two seconds,The color of the object was described as orange,The observation lasted for about one minute,There was physical evidence related to the sighting,The object went out of sight behind some trees.
witness description: Two individuals, including a 14-year-old boy, observed the object together.
